  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Regina Mauskopf.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Regina Helman.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Solocin, Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1917.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's July 13th.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father was Nathan Helman.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother's maiden name was Rose [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Klineman ?].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were nine-- nine children-- eight siblings.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was the ninth.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The oldest is Yosl, and Yankel and [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Freida, ?] and [INAUDIBLE], and [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Mil ?], and Malka, [INAUDIBLE], and Lesier.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm 79.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I have-- the oldest was like 1895 or '96.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then Yankel was born like two-- two years after.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Freida ?] was, I think, [? 1900, ?] I think.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then it was [INAUDIBLE] in '91, '92.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then was [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Mil, ?] but-- I mean, 190--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Three.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Three or four.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then Malka was born on 1909.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE] was born in 1911, and Leiser in 1913.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'Solechin.'",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there was not too many-- just about 11 Jewish families.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And life was very nice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's country thing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were-- one of-- one of the Jewish people had a grocery store.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's all, what it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were very happy, like really happy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was-- everybody had fields.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they had the-- the necessary things like was from-- from the-- like-- it's not like farmers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But on the smaller range, everybody had their own [? farm-- ?] [?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I know ?] from on year to another whatever was grown in the ground.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I was doing the work, especially in the war when it came.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was nobody to hire, because everybody was gone.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The brothers were gone, which they use to come and help.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I did a lot of work with my father.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was-- he was a foreman by deforestation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know how to explain that, the how--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Lumber, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Lumber business, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
